[{"******* topictree/  (for root) levels=2 "}]

[{"******* the usecase for topictree is probably only guis, people who just want some data will use the tables/ endpoint"}]

[{"******* we must choose included vs nested for the api"}]
[{"the data in the included approach is close to data in an sql-database, (but) with the id's of the children in the record."}]

[{"*******included is"},{{"simpler code(?)"},{"easier to read big datasets for humans"},{"Lets you render the first level without reading the whole dataset"}]
[{"*******nested is"},{"less verbose"},{"easier to read small datasets for humans"} ]

